title: Move It: Moving & Delivery
description:
Move It connects you to reliable Pros & Muscles that make moving out, pickup, delivery, and junk removal as easy as ever. Forget about endlessly contacting moving companies and waiting for quotes. Renting a U-Haul is inconvenient and costs more anyway. With Move It you can get connected with experienced movers that make pick up and delivery completely stress free.

Simply tell us when, where, and what you need delivered, select how many helpers you need, and get an instant guaranteed price quote. Enjoy quality same day delivery from our team of Pros and Muscles — professionals ready to deliver your items at a moment’s notice. It’s time to say goodbye to DIY moving and truck rental. Move It takes care of it all.

Enjoy quick and easy booking and let seasoned Pros deliver your items. Whether an apartment move, office move, storage unit pickup, or just hauling heavy items, Move It has you covered. Welcome to a delivery service that simplifies moving and makes your life easier.

Truck & Muscle Anytime You Need It™ with Move It’s on demand moving and delivery app.

MOVE IT FEATURES

ON-DEMAND MOVING, DELIVERY & MORE
- Moving Service: Office move, apartment move, or storage unit move. Our professionals have you covered. 
- On Demand Delivery: Reliable delivery when you need it most. Let our Pros deliver your items from any store you need.
- Junk Removal: Get rid of those unused and unwanted heavy items. Clean the garage out. Best price guarantee. 
- Move It is cheaper and more convenient than any expensive truck rental service

QUICK & EASY BOOKING
- Get connected with movers and other professionals right away
- No hidden fees. Guaranteed pricing. No hourly minimums. 
- Pay and tip directly in app for added convenience

GUARANTEED PRICING FOR YOUR DELIVERY
- Get a guaranteed quote when you book
- Save up to 50-80% compared to a traditional moving and delivery company
- No more haggling with expensive moving services

REAL TIME TRACKING
- Know where your items are with the help of our moving and delivery app
- Monitor the status of your store delivery or moving service with real-time tracking
- Enjoy a stress free experience getting moving help.

MOVING SERVICE YOU CAN TRUST
- All Move It Pros & Muscles are reviewed by customers just like you 
- Review what others have rated before you accept a moving or delivery service
- Help other Move It users by leaving your own review

SAFE MOVING & DELIVERY
- Every item is backed by our top of the line, limited commercial insurance policy
- All Move It Pros & Muscles have been through a strict background check process
- No worrying about who will handle and deliver your items with Move It.

Move It has a commitment to excellence and thrives on our customers’ happiness and satisfaction.

Move It is currently in the Las Vegas valley, San Diego County, Tucson, Denver, and Phoenix areas.

Move It expects to be in every major city in 2024.
